Install guide
=============

1. Create a MySQL database and user;
2. Import database.sql dump;
3. Copy dnsmanager to /var/www for example and configure apache to point this directory;
4. Edit index.php and set the correct db credentials and your nameserver FQDN and external ip;
5. Edit application/cron.php and set the same information as above and to zone.conf and db directory, where db files will be stored;
6. Include zone.conf into your named.conf file;
7. Execute "chmod +x application/cron.php";
8. Add new cron task "/path/to/cron.php -c processqueue" with interval 5 minutes;

*WARNING! Webclient has no authentication, so ensure that webclient is not accessed from external network or protect it with apache mod_auth!*